title: War of the Roses: Was the Picture Really from 10 Years Ago?
description: Marcie found a risque picture on her boyfriend's computer of a girl he claims he dated 10 years ago.  She feels like it might be from something more recent but doesn't know for sure so she wants to do War of the Roses to figure out if he's cheating.
